_sText:
Ported from TF2. Added 16 new songs!

This is a Singleplayer only map. It was inspired by lasers from Zombie Escape/Deathrun maps. But on this map lasers spawn in a rhythm with the music.

To select a chart, shoot or hit the panel with the said chart.
You can use modifiers to make your life easier/harder

This map has about 40 songs ranging from easy charts to really REALLY hard ones
